WEBVTT

00:46.620 --> 00:47.760
This way!

01:33.530 --> 01:34.670
Are you okay?

01:35.380 --> 01:36.249
I'm fine.

01:36.250 --> 01:37.930
Officer Chen, why are you here?

01:40.220 --> 01:42.170
Why is my Pomegranate Jade with you?

01:43.880 --> 01:45.339
It broke, right?

01:45.340 --> 01:47.269
So, I wanted to fix it.

01:47.270 --> 01:48.819
But I still couldn't fix it

01:48.820 --> 01:50.400
despite working on it for so long.

01:51.820 --> 01:53.320
But don't worry.

01:53.350 --> 01:55.030
I'll get it fixed.

02:01.070 --> 02:02.320
Where are they?

02:02.820 --> 02:03.960
Check over there!

02:05.220 --> 02:06.360
Hurry up!

02:08.380 --> 02:09.520
Open the door!

02:09.570 --> 02:10.990
(Qing)

02:11.150 --> 02:12.869
Do you think you can get rid of me

02:12.870 --> 02:14.530
with just a gold badge?

02:17.570 --> 02:18.579
You wench, I'll kill you.

02:18.580 --> 02:19.619
You fool!

02:19.620 --> 02:20.619
Don't be so blind.

02:20.620 --> 02:21.499
Sorry

02:21.500 --> 02:22.640
for offending you.

03:46.090 --> 03:50.409
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:50.410 --> 03:53.670
=Episode 23=

03:55.300 --> 03:56.440
Your Ladyship.

03:58.610 --> 04:01.630
Our men are guarding
the outer east, west, and south gates.

04:01.640 --> 04:04.400
Except for the corner gate that leads
to the Duke of Ying's Residence.

04:04.410 --> 04:06.619
But that gate is always closed.

04:06.620 --> 04:08.280
Is Duke of Ying
in his residence tonight?

04:08.340 --> 04:09.530
According to his servants,

04:09.580 --> 04:11.949
he is patrolling the south gate tonight.

04:11.950 --> 04:13.130
So, he's not in his residence.

04:14.710 --> 04:16.600
He went to the south gate for no reason.

04:17.600 --> 04:19.530
And the northern city is on fire.

04:21.700 --> 04:22.920
This is not right.

04:24.550 --> 04:25.690
Open the gate!

04:26.620 --> 04:27.760
Open the gate!

04:28.500 --> 04:29.640
Wait!

04:30.380 --> 04:31.520
Open the gate!

04:34.590 --> 04:35.589
Who are you?

04:35.590 --> 04:36.730
Your Ladyship.

04:36.940 --> 04:38.499
I work for Duke of Ying.

04:38.500 --> 04:39.890
There's a fire outside.

04:40.110 --> 04:42.170
His Grace is worried about you.

04:42.570 --> 04:44.210
So, he has sent us here to check on you.

04:44.430 --> 04:47.120
Hurry up and get some poles
to bar the gate.

04:48.390 --> 04:50.960
The Duke of Ying's Residence and
Yizhi Hall are united in public.

04:50.990 --> 04:52.680
But we are actually sworn enemies.

04:52.690 --> 04:54.780
My eldest uncle will not
send someone to check on us.

04:54.790 --> 04:55.730
Open the gate!

04:55.740 --> 04:58.669
- They are not his guards.
- Open the gate!

04:58.670 --> 05:00.440
Your Ladyship!
Something bad has happened!

05:01.390 --> 05:02.549
A group of bandits

05:02.550 --> 05:04.469
are causing chaos on the street.

05:04.470 --> 05:05.610
Bandits?

05:06.230 --> 05:07.079
Open the gate!

05:07.080 --> 05:08.950
(Yizhi Hall)

05:09.020 --> 05:10.440
Open the gate now!

05:10.450 --> 05:11.589
- Are you sure?
- Open the gate!

05:11.590 --> 05:13.299
- The city gate should be closed.
- Open the gate!

05:13.300 --> 05:14.650
How can the bandits enter the city?

05:14.660 --> 05:15.909
I saw them on the roof.

05:15.910 --> 05:17.029
Of course I'm sure.

05:17.030 --> 05:18.770
Our backdoor is also blocked
by the bandits.

05:18.780 --> 05:20.989
What about the corner gate that connects
us to the Duke of Ying's Residence?

05:20.990 --> 05:22.910
There are many guards there
with more than enough weapons.

05:22.920 --> 05:24.739
It's locked.
And no one is responding to us.

05:24.740 --> 05:26.170
We are trapped here.

05:28.110 --> 05:29.979
- Open the door now!
- Break it down!

05:29.980 --> 05:30.899
Roger that!

05:30.900 --> 05:32.230
(Yizhi Hall)

05:36.700 --> 05:37.840
Hang in there.

05:39.740 --> 05:42.179
You. Bring our men
from the west gate here.

05:42.180 --> 05:43.310
- Roger that.
- Hurry up.

05:43.320 --> 05:45.270
The Duke of Ying's Residence
must be behind this.

05:45.280 --> 05:47.480
Should we fire a signal
to inform His Lordship?

05:48.790 --> 05:49.739
I'll look for the flare.

05:49.740 --> 05:50.589
Open the gate!

05:50.590 --> 05:52.350
(Yizhi Hall)
Open the gate!

05:53.590 --> 05:54.730
Wait.

05:55.060 --> 05:56.200
Come back.

05:57.690 --> 06:00.210
First, they lured him away
with the fire in the northern city.

06:00.470 --> 06:02.139
Now, the bandits
have entered the Capital

06:02.140 --> 06:03.410
with no one preventing them.

06:03.590 --> 06:05.669
- Someone must have planned this.
- Break it down.

06:05.670 --> 06:07.220
If His Lordship rushes back,

06:07.500 --> 06:09.299
he'll be charged with deserting his duty

06:09.300 --> 06:10.600
and deceiving His Majesty.

06:11.060 --> 06:13.170
Worse, he can be charged with treason.

06:13.790 --> 06:14.930
Hit it with all your might.

06:15.030 --> 06:16.739
The rest of you, climb the wall.

06:16.740 --> 06:17.880
Roger that!

06:18.790 --> 06:20.059
- Hurry up!
- Hurry up!

06:20.060 --> 06:21.200
Get up.

06:21.430 --> 06:22.570
Watch it.

06:22.930 --> 06:24.290
There's someone on the wall!

06:30.940 --> 06:32.669
- Your Lordship.
- How's Her Ladyship?

06:32.670 --> 06:33.850
Where's the Military Command?

06:33.990 --> 06:34.869
Your Lordship.

06:34.870 --> 06:37.710
The Military Command
hasn't sent any reports.

06:38.170 --> 06:40.230
Criminals will take advantage
of this fire for sure.

06:40.240 --> 06:41.540
Why hasn't he reported anything?

06:42.550 --> 06:44.290
The Military Command is useless.

06:44.500 --> 06:45.280
Your Lordship.

06:45.290 --> 06:47.270
Her Ladyship has always
been wise and resourceful.

06:47.280 --> 06:49.549
Besides, General Yan
is guarding the residence.

06:49.550 --> 06:51.040
Her Ladyship has the flares with her.

06:51.090 --> 06:51.999
If she's in danger,

06:52.000 --> 06:53.600
she'll send us a signal.

06:54.670 --> 06:56.809
If Ms. Longevity knows
that this is done on purpose

06:56.810 --> 06:58.299
to make me be absent without leave,

06:58.300 --> 07:00.120
she won't fire the flare.

07:01.350 --> 07:02.500
I have to go back.

07:03.430 --> 07:04.570
Your Lordship.

07:04.830 --> 07:06.130
You can't do that, Your Lordship.

07:06.220 --> 07:08.369
We are the Imperial Guard of the palace.

07:08.370 --> 07:10.499
If we leave without informing
His Majesty about it,

07:10.500 --> 07:12.770
we'll be charged for treason.

07:13.940 --> 07:16.170
Hurry up! Push them down!

07:19.820 --> 07:21.240
How long can we hold them back?

07:25.140 --> 07:26.730
You hurt so many of my men.

07:27.180 --> 07:28.320
Your Ladyship.

07:28.590 --> 07:30.909
I'm told that you are a wealthy person.

07:30.910 --> 07:33.850
We just want to make a living.

07:34.740 --> 07:36.600
We just want to borrow some money.

07:37.140 --> 07:39.000
If you give us the money,

07:39.010 --> 07:40.660
- Your Ladyship.
- we'll spare your life.

07:40.670 --> 07:41.920
Change into a maid's outfit.

07:42.030 --> 07:43.549
My sister and I will do our best

07:43.550 --> 07:45.920
to help you escape even
if it'll cost us our lives.

07:46.940 --> 07:48.080
I'm the lady of the house.

07:48.620 --> 07:50.549
If I leave,
people will lose their morale.

07:50.550 --> 07:51.970
And everyone will die.

07:52.390 --> 07:54.120
Besides, the street
is full of bandits now.

07:54.140 --> 07:55.560
It may be safer in the residence.

07:56.590 --> 07:58.299
There are three factors
in winning a fight.

07:58.300 --> 07:59.429
First, courage.

07:59.430 --> 08:00.299
Second, location.

08:00.300 --> 08:01.149
And third, situation.

08:01.150 --> 08:02.469
(Yizhi Hall)
This is our home.

08:02.470 --> 08:03.990
All three factors are to our advantage.

08:04.000 --> 08:05.379
If we give it our all to fight,

08:05.380 --> 08:06.650
we may win.

08:06.670 --> 08:07.669
Your Ladyship.

08:07.670 --> 08:09.040
Just say the word

08:09.180 --> 08:10.680
and we'll fight to the end with them.

08:12.500 --> 08:13.349
Attack!

08:13.350 --> 08:15.170
If they dare to barge in,

08:15.740 --> 08:18.000
we'll eliminate them all.

08:19.430 --> 08:20.570
Mr. Chen.

08:22.590 --> 08:23.589
Your Ladyship.

08:23.590 --> 08:25.600
You know the layout
of the residence the best.

08:25.990 --> 08:28.360
Try and bring us some backups
from Zhaowen Bookstore.

08:28.430 --> 08:29.499
Your Ladyship.

08:29.500 --> 08:31.799
His Lordship entrusted your safety to me

08:31.800 --> 08:34.310
when he left the residence.

08:34.370 --> 08:36.290
I'll protect you

08:36.500 --> 08:38.659
at the cost of my life.

08:38.660 --> 08:39.800
This is an emergency.

08:40.230 --> 08:41.139
I'll find a way

08:41.140 --> 08:43.130
to inform Mr. Yan
to bring some guards with him.

08:43.190 --> 08:44.909
But there are many bandits here.

08:44.910 --> 08:46.630
I'm just worried
that they'll have a plan B

08:46.640 --> 08:48.380
to take down Yizhi Hall.

08:49.990 --> 08:52.259
I think the gate can hold
for a while longer.

08:52.260 --> 08:53.960
Let's go according to my plan first.

08:54.230 --> 08:55.610
I won't let you down.

09:01.830 --> 09:04.069
Su Xin. Send someone to get
the firewood from the shed.

09:04.070 --> 09:05.379
Pile it in the middle
of the courtyard and light it up.

09:05.380 --> 09:07.060
When Mr. Yan and
the others see the fire,

09:07.070 --> 09:08.150
they'll come and rescue us.

09:08.160 --> 09:09.189
Yes, Your Ladyship.

09:09.190 --> 09:10.139
Su Lan.

09:10.140 --> 09:12.189
Send someone to wet
all the firewood sheds.

09:12.190 --> 09:14.250
Then use heavy furniture
to block the door.

09:14.420 --> 09:17.250
Ask the kitchen maids
to start boiling oil.

09:17.470 --> 09:18.610
Yes, Your Ladyship.

09:18.710 --> 09:19.890
Come with me.

09:36.750 --> 09:37.890
Shh.

09:39.380 --> 09:40.520
Hurry up.

09:40.660 --> 09:41.800
Hurry up.

09:52.830 --> 09:53.970
What are you doing?

10:02.020 --> 10:03.160
Move aside!

10:04.190 --> 10:06.419
Boss. The west gate has been breached.

10:06.420 --> 10:07.259
Good.

10:07.260 --> 10:08.539
(Yizhi Hall)
Continue to break this gate down.

10:08.540 --> 10:09.829
Others, come with me.

10:09.830 --> 10:10.739
Yes!

10:10.740 --> 10:11.880
Let's go!

10:14.770 --> 10:17.110
(Natural Grace and Talent)

10:22.830 --> 10:24.560
Your Ladyship!

10:24.770 --> 10:26.109
The west gate has been breached!

10:26.110 --> 10:27.770
The bandits are pouring in now.

10:28.500 --> 10:30.250
We can't fight them face-on.

10:30.310 --> 10:32.189
Take the weak and women
to hide in the cellar.

10:32.190 --> 10:33.109
Don't make any noise.

10:33.110 --> 10:34.750
Others get into the firewood shed with me.

10:34.760 --> 10:35.509
Let's go.

10:35.510 --> 10:36.660
Let's go.

10:40.310 --> 10:41.610
- Boss.
- Boss.

10:43.660 --> 10:45.309
Ask our men in the east and west gate

10:45.310 --> 10:46.499
to guard the gates.

10:46.500 --> 10:48.619
You, go in and search for money.

10:48.620 --> 10:51.370
- Yes, Boss!
- As for the rest, find the people here.

10:51.660 --> 10:53.040
- Let's go!
- Yes, Boss!

10:55.110 --> 10:56.530
Hurry up, over there!

10:57.020 --> 10:58.410
General Yan, look.

10:58.660 --> 11:00.610
Why is there smoke
coming out of Yizhi Hall?

11:04.420 --> 11:06.010
She's at the end of the rope.

11:06.710 --> 11:08.709
But she lit up a pyre

11:08.710 --> 11:10.440
to light up the way for us.

11:11.900 --> 11:13.019
Split up and look for them!

11:13.020 --> 11:13.989
Yes, Boss!

11:13.990 --> 11:15.069
Come with me.

11:15.070 --> 11:16.210
- Roger that!
- Roger that!

11:18.540 --> 11:20.010
Boss, over here!

11:21.230 --> 11:22.410
They are all inside.

11:23.190 --> 11:25.019
But this shed is wet with water.

11:25.020 --> 11:26.949
We can't light it up so easily.

11:26.950 --> 11:29.040
Your Ladyship,
there are many of them outside.

11:29.500 --> 11:32.370
Just some women hiding inside in fear.

11:32.420 --> 11:34.290
They can't escape.

11:38.310 --> 11:39.450
Your Ladyship.

11:39.830 --> 11:42.080
You are quite the heroine.

11:42.260 --> 11:46.080
Unfortunately, someone wants you dead.

11:47.420 --> 11:48.770
This is my first time.

11:48.900 --> 11:50.040
It's okay.

11:50.380 --> 11:51.520
Focus.

11:52.620 --> 11:53.770
Stare at your target.

11:55.830 --> 11:56.970
Aim.

12:00.740 --> 12:03.680
It's normal to be scared
for the first time.

12:04.260 --> 12:06.960
But the more afraid you are,
the calmer you should be.

12:07.470 --> 12:08.610
Clear your mind.

12:09.500 --> 12:12.650
Don't worry. I'm with you.

12:31.970 --> 12:33.820
I just need to take down
the ringleader first.

12:33.900 --> 12:35.499
We don't know who will die here today.

12:35.500 --> 12:37.130
Boss, are you okay?

12:37.710 --> 12:38.470
You are so useless.

12:38.480 --> 12:40.600
Why didn't you tell me
that they have a hand cannon?

12:40.610 --> 12:41.169
Your Ladyship.

12:41.170 --> 12:42.840
You hit the person beside him.

12:45.800 --> 12:46.950
Attack.

12:49.950 --> 12:51.250
What kind of residence is this?

12:51.590 --> 12:53.960
They have five hand cannons.

12:54.350 --> 12:57.010
Aren't they afraid
that their weapons will be confiscated?

12:57.020 --> 12:58.160
Shoot!

13:01.540 --> 13:02.960
Those with shields, attack!

13:17.050 --> 13:19.440
Your Ladyship, we only have
one shot left. What should we do?

13:19.590 --> 13:20.770
We stay still for now.

13:21.270 --> 13:23.010
As long as they stay back
for fear of us,

13:23.380 --> 13:25.200
someone will come to our rescue.

14:01.850 --> 14:03.949
- Come with me to rescue Her Ladyship.
- Roger that.

14:03.950 --> 14:05.840
- The rest, protect the villagers.
- Roger that!

14:30.170 --> 14:32.419
- Where's Her Ladyship?
- She's still in the residence.

14:32.420 --> 14:34.250
Let's get rid of these bandits first.

14:34.310 --> 14:35.450
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

14:35.660 --> 14:36.589
Boss.

14:36.590 --> 14:37.829
We are in trouble.

14:37.830 --> 14:40.800
Someone is attacking
from the west and main gate.

14:41.540 --> 14:42.379
Boss.

14:42.380 --> 14:43.469
We are tricked.

14:43.470 --> 14:45.259
They are just trying to buy time.

14:45.260 --> 14:46.610
Let's retreat now.

14:47.010 --> 14:48.360
Darn it.

14:48.710 --> 14:49.850
Looks like

14:50.590 --> 14:53.650
I've been set up
by Wang Yingxue again.

14:55.070 --> 14:56.210
Retreat!

15:05.260 --> 15:06.770
Your Ladyship, they have retreated.

15:14.950 --> 15:16.090
Ms. Longevity!

15:18.230 --> 15:19.370
Your Lordship.

15:20.780 --> 15:21.659
Where's her Ladyship?

15:21.660 --> 15:22.890
She's in her room.

15:23.020 --> 15:23.949
Your Lordship.

15:23.950 --> 15:25.779
It was unfortunate that you weren't here

15:25.780 --> 15:27.750
to witness her magnificence.

15:27.780 --> 15:31.379
She managed to hold them back with just
some servants and maidservants.

15:31.380 --> 15:32.309
What's our casualty?

15:32.310 --> 15:34.170
Eight guards are hurt
and two are crippled.

15:34.290 --> 15:36.060
They managed to hold back
dozens of bandits.

15:39.520 --> 15:41.019
Do these bodies belong to the bandits?

15:41.020 --> 15:42.160
Yes.

15:50.970 --> 15:52.380
You don't have to follow me anymore.

15:57.150 --> 15:58.829
- Your Lordship.
- Is her Ladyship inside?

15:58.830 --> 15:59.970
Yes.

16:17.190 --> 16:18.330
Ms. Longevity.

16:23.070 --> 16:24.309
Why are you back?

16:24.310 --> 16:25.650
I saw that the city was on fire.

16:25.660 --> 16:27.960
So, I came back in case
you were in trouble.

16:32.470 --> 16:34.010
The servants told me

16:34.350 --> 16:35.650
that my heroine

16:35.980 --> 16:37.920
commanded them fiercely
and defeated the bandits

16:38.110 --> 16:39.370
despite their greater number.

16:39.900 --> 16:41.320
You were amazing.

16:49.110 --> 16:50.720
Why are you crying?

16:51.350 --> 16:53.250
I don't know.

16:53.590 --> 16:56.010
I didn't want to cry
when I faced the bandits.

16:56.110 --> 16:58.920
But I want to cry when I see you.

17:01.590 --> 17:02.659
I'm sorry.

17:02.660 --> 17:03.840
It was my fault.

17:04.980 --> 17:06.610
I should've come back earlier.

17:57.550 --> 17:58.760
Back then, I married you

17:59.510 --> 18:01.000
to protect you.

18:01.590 --> 18:03.200
But now, you were in danger

18:03.830 --> 18:05.370
because of me.

18:07.220 --> 18:09.000
How do you know it was because of you?

18:09.460 --> 18:10.600
Maybe

18:11.110 --> 18:13.440
the bandits were just interested
in my dowry?

18:19.660 --> 18:20.800
By the way,

18:21.110 --> 18:23.939
aren't you supposed to guard
the Western Mountain Palace?

18:23.940 --> 18:25.440
Why did you come back out of the blue?

18:27.270 --> 18:28.410
Don't worry.

18:28.980 --> 18:30.240
I came back alone.

18:30.960 --> 18:32.950
The Imperial Guard
will protect the palace.

18:33.870 --> 18:35.920
We are the Imperial Guard of the palace.

18:36.020 --> 18:38.570
If we leave without informing
His Majesty about it,

18:38.690 --> 18:40.469
we'll be charged for treason.

18:40.470 --> 18:41.610
Lu Ming, here's my order.

18:41.900 --> 18:43.029
Yes, Your Lordship.

18:43.030 --> 18:46.440
Lead the Imperial Guard
to protect the palace.

18:46.450 --> 18:47.820
Make sure to guard the palace well.

18:48.270 --> 18:49.410
Your Lordship.

18:52.980 --> 18:54.869
So, the elites of the Ding Army

18:54.870 --> 18:56.720
are in the Capital.

18:57.900 --> 18:58.899
Yes.

18:58.900 --> 19:01.749
It doesn't matter if they are
in Futing or the Capital.

19:01.750 --> 19:04.170
They will always serve their country

19:04.180 --> 19:06.000
and defend our people.

19:06.460 --> 19:08.000
I know that.

19:08.660 --> 19:10.269
But you can't let anyone know

19:10.270 --> 19:11.829
that the elites of the Ding Army

19:11.830 --> 19:13.560
are in the Capital.

19:14.620 --> 19:16.810
You better get back
to the Western Mountain Palace.

19:17.460 --> 19:18.890
I don't want anything to go wrong.

19:37.010 --> 19:39.070
(Peace and Harmony)

19:46.750 --> 19:47.920
May God protect us.

19:48.140 --> 19:49.480
May the Duke of Ding protect us.

19:50.140 --> 19:51.069
Your Lordship.

19:51.070 --> 19:53.170
Please come back quickly.

19:57.420 --> 19:58.560
Your Lordship.

20:28.830 --> 20:29.970
Who is it?

20:48.460 --> 20:49.600
Your Lordship.

20:49.830 --> 20:50.970
Interrogate them.

20:51.350 --> 20:53.309
Let's see if they are bandits or moles.

20:53.310 --> 20:54.159
Yes, Your Lordship.

20:54.160 --> 20:55.419
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

20:55.420 --> 20:56.560
Your Ladyship.

20:57.380 --> 20:58.309
- Look.
- Kneel.

20:58.310 --> 20:59.650
She's trying to run away.

20:59.700 --> 21:00.850
It's chaotic outside.

21:01.220 --> 21:02.850
Where are you going to escape to?

21:04.550 --> 21:06.869
Where does the money come from?

21:06.870 --> 21:07.709
Your Ladyship.

21:07.710 --> 21:08.800
Your Mother, Madam Wang,

21:08.810 --> 21:11.010
asked me to take His Lordship's
badge to leave the city.

21:11.020 --> 21:12.769
I don't know about anything else.

21:12.770 --> 21:14.139
I'm sorry.

21:14.140 --> 21:16.050
(My mother took
His Lordship's official badge?)

21:18.700 --> 21:20.340
Ready a carriage for me right now.

21:20.350 --> 21:21.829
- It's chaotic outside.
- Your Ladyship.

21:21.830 --> 21:23.219
Your Ladyship, where are you going?

21:23.220 --> 21:24.059
- I need to get to His Lordship.
- Your Ladyship.

21:24.060 --> 21:25.440
Let me go on behalf of you.

21:25.980 --> 21:27.549
You can't save His Lordship.

21:27.550 --> 21:28.399
How about this?

21:28.400 --> 21:29.829
Bring all the guards with us

21:29.830 --> 21:30.729
to escort us.

21:30.730 --> 21:31.870
Yes, Your Ladyship.

21:32.140 --> 21:33.280
What?

21:33.510 --> 21:35.170
We agreed on 30 to 40 people

21:35.970 --> 21:37.480
who would leave after killing Dou Zhao.

21:37.590 --> 21:39.480
But more than 200 bandits came.

21:39.870 --> 21:41.610
That's treason.

21:42.070 --> 21:44.410
It was indeed quite a mess.

21:44.620 --> 21:46.130
But that wench must be dead

21:46.830 --> 21:49.050
after getting attacked
by so many people.

21:49.900 --> 21:51.280
We are doomed too.

21:51.900 --> 21:55.050
Something so major has happened
under His Majesty's watch.

21:55.830 --> 21:57.789
They'll get to the bottom of this.

21:57.790 --> 21:59.130
Don't worry, Madam.

21:59.180 --> 22:01.869
The commanders of the Military Command
are at the Drunken Bordello.

22:01.870 --> 22:03.419
When they realize it,

22:03.420 --> 22:05.109
the bandits will be gone by then.

22:05.110 --> 22:07.890
They won't be suspicious of us.

22:10.140 --> 22:11.280
You are right.

22:22.340 --> 22:23.480
I need to thank you

22:24.660 --> 22:26.000
for this.

22:26.510 --> 22:27.760
This is just my job.

22:41.700 --> 22:43.459
Your Ladyship,
I've gotten the information.

22:43.460 --> 22:45.390
His Lordship is drinking
at the Drunken Bordello.

22:45.400 --> 22:47.440
Okay. Hurry up.

22:49.070 --> 22:50.330
Hurry up!

22:56.310 --> 22:57.450
Stop right there!

22:57.510 --> 22:58.680
Stay away!

23:02.510 --> 23:03.699
Stop that carriage!

23:03.700 --> 23:05.130
We can't go back empty-handed.

23:06.310 --> 23:07.450
Stop the carriage!

23:08.420 --> 23:11.330
(Duke of Jining's Residence)
It's the Duke of Jining's carriage.

23:13.310 --> 23:15.269
You are Wang Yingxue's
youngest daughter.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.309
Catch her!

23:16.310 --> 23:17.480
Run, Your Ladyship!

23:28.110 --> 23:31.000
May I escape the fire pit of hell

23:31.070 --> 23:33.920
and have my sins erased.

23:55.650 --> 23:56.880
Tingyu.

24:01.790 --> 24:03.330
Little girl.

24:03.790 --> 24:05.410
You have nowhere to run now.

24:07.810 --> 24:09.139
Come home with me.

24:09.140 --> 24:11.549
I can give you as much money
as you want.

24:11.550 --> 24:12.960
I don't want money.

24:12.980 --> 24:14.200
I want you.

24:19.750 --> 24:20.890
You wench.

24:23.030 --> 24:24.480
You'll pay for your mother's sins.

24:24.790 --> 24:27.920
Blame your mother for this.

24:34.980 --> 24:36.120
Let's go.

25:14.750 --> 25:15.890
Your Lordship.

25:16.660 --> 25:17.460
Let's go.

25:17.470 --> 25:19.309
- Let's drink until we drop.
- Let's continue.

25:19.310 --> 25:20.379
Let's drink until we drop.

25:20.380 --> 25:21.690
- Let's go.
- Let's keep drinking.

25:21.700 --> 25:23.060
- Let's keep drinking.
- Let's go.

25:35.420 --> 25:37.570
- Great!
- Great!

26:10.290 --> 26:16.190
(Zhou Jiaxin)

26:42.870 --> 26:44.010
Your Lordship.

26:56.550 --> 26:57.690
Your Lordship.

27:01.310 --> 27:02.450
Eunuch Wang.

27:04.680 --> 27:06.960
Why are you here so late at night?

27:07.900 --> 27:09.130
Your Lordship.

27:09.460 --> 27:13.000
Her Majesty has asked me
to bring you some food.

27:15.110 --> 27:16.219
Thank you, Eunuch Wang.

27:16.220 --> 27:17.609
Relay my thanks to Her Majesty.

27:17.610 --> 27:20.190
(Flow of Colors)

27:21.900 --> 27:23.040
Your Ladyship.

27:23.120 --> 27:24.219
General Yan.

27:24.220 --> 27:26.309
We have locked them up
and interrogated them.

27:26.310 --> 27:28.000
They work for the Duke of Ying.

27:28.070 --> 27:28.939
Also,

27:28.940 --> 27:30.929
we found this from the Cangbei Gang.

27:30.930 --> 27:33.670
(Wei Tingyu)

27:33.700 --> 27:35.090
Wei Tingyu.

27:35.700 --> 27:38.309
The Military Command
is supposed to be on duty.

27:38.310 --> 27:39.610
But we've received news

27:39.900 --> 27:41.619
that the Duke of Jining
and his troops

27:41.620 --> 27:43.939
are drinking and enjoying themselves
in the southern city.

27:43.940 --> 27:46.640
It's no wonder that they can't hear
the pleas coming from the northern city.

27:46.650 --> 27:48.650
Those commanders
are used to having it their way.

27:48.680 --> 27:51.620
I'm afraid that their subordinates
didn't even dare to report it to them.

27:54.660 --> 27:56.589
Your Ladyship, what happened?

27:56.590 --> 27:58.699
That's what I want to ask you.

27:58.700 --> 28:00.179
Why are you questioning me instead?

28:00.180 --> 28:02.160
Your Ladyship, it was our fault.

28:02.170 --> 28:03.719
We were focused on putting out the fire.

28:03.720 --> 28:06.020
So, we opened the corner gate
and the bandits managed to get in.

28:06.030 --> 28:07.029
I don't know what Mr. Yan

28:07.030 --> 28:08.459
found out

28:08.460 --> 28:09.570
from those bandits.

28:09.580 --> 28:12.269
But don't let it drive a wedge between
the Duke of Ying's Residence

28:12.270 --> 28:14.090
and Yizhi Hall and break
His Lordship's heart.

28:14.110 --> 28:15.470
When the bandits were attacking,

28:15.480 --> 28:17.589
we went to the Duke of Ying's Residence
to borrow some weapons.

28:17.590 --> 28:18.510
But it was bolted down.

28:18.520 --> 28:19.899
When Her Ladyship
secured the south gate,

28:19.900 --> 28:22.269
the corner door was left open
and the bandits came out of nowhere.

28:22.270 --> 28:23.789
It was too much of a coincidence.

28:23.790 --> 28:25.269
Your Ladyship, yes.

28:25.270 --> 28:27.139
From what I know,
the bandits from Cangzhou

28:27.140 --> 28:28.419
were targeting your dowry.

28:28.420 --> 28:30.450
Your Ladyship, please stop.

28:34.510 --> 28:35.650
You scoundrel.

28:46.380 --> 28:48.200
Where did the bandits come from?

28:48.590 --> 28:49.619
Didn't they know

28:49.620 --> 28:50.850
whose residence is this?

28:51.140 --> 28:52.760
They went crazy over money.

28:58.180 --> 28:59.330
Cousin-in-law.

28:59.460 --> 29:00.610
Don't worry.

29:00.790 --> 29:03.200
Yantang will take over this matter soon.

29:08.420 --> 29:11.520
Butler Lyu opened the corner gate
to get water to put out the fire.

29:12.030 --> 29:14.570
It's unfortunate
that something went wrong.

29:16.940 --> 29:19.440
Do you know how many people
were killed and injured

29:19.900 --> 29:21.850
by the bandits tonight?

29:22.420 --> 29:23.899
Everyone in Yizhi Hall

29:23.900 --> 29:25.619
almost lost their lives.

29:25.620 --> 29:27.309
It's not an issue that can be dropped

29:27.310 --> 29:29.090
just by saying that it was a mistake.

29:29.500 --> 29:31.810
Someone needs to be held responsible
for the lost lives.

29:40.620 --> 29:42.899
Mother, this is their family's matter.

29:42.900 --> 29:44.379
Our uncle is using us as a shield

29:44.380 --> 29:45.699
between them.

29:45.700 --> 29:46.840
We better

29:47.270 --> 29:49.130
stay out of this.

29:53.740 --> 29:56.090
After all, I'm from a humble family.

29:56.180 --> 29:58.280
I don't know the severity
of this matter.

30:00.030 --> 30:01.069
Go and bring me

30:01.070 --> 30:02.979
my matching token.

30:02.980 --> 30:04.120
Yes, Madam.

30:12.660 --> 30:14.170
I'm not capable enough to handle this.

30:14.180 --> 30:16.720
Please take over
the Duke of Ying's Residence

30:16.930 --> 30:19.330
and settle this issue
to help a fellow relative.

30:19.900 --> 30:21.040
Cousin-in-law.

30:22.330 --> 30:25.430
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

30:32.080 --> 30:33.220
Your Ladyship.

30:35.070 --> 30:36.720
Are you from the northern city?

30:36.740 --> 30:37.619
Yes.

30:37.620 --> 30:39.820
Why didn't you report it
when the bandits entered the city?

30:39.830 --> 30:42.179
Military Command officers
were drinking in the backyard.

30:42.180 --> 30:44.280
We were ordered not to disturb them.

30:44.350 --> 30:45.789
We are just low-rank officers.

30:45.790 --> 30:47.510
We didn't dare
to go against their order.

30:48.940 --> 30:50.130
I'll take you to them.

30:55.590 --> 30:56.730
Nice!

30:58.220 --> 31:00.789
- None of you are allowed to leave
- Good!

31:00.790 --> 31:02.379
until you've finished all the wine here.

31:02.380 --> 31:04.170
Nice. Cheers!

31:05.420 --> 31:06.720
Cheers!

31:06.790 --> 31:07.899
Let's have another one.

31:07.900 --> 31:09.890
- Come, Duke.
- Refill their wine cups.

31:11.350 --> 31:12.680
Refill their wine cups.

31:18.380 --> 31:19.229
Come.

31:19.230 --> 31:20.840
Let's drink another cup.

31:32.750 --> 31:33.890
Dou Zhao?

31:37.980 --> 31:38.969
Your Ladyship.

31:38.970 --> 31:40.409
Are you trying to kill an official

31:40.410 --> 31:42.290
just because your husband
holds a lot of power?

31:42.350 --> 31:45.180
The duties of the Military Command
are to take down criminals

31:45.330 --> 31:46.710
and protect the city.

31:47.410 --> 31:49.350
Now, hundreds of bandits
have entered the city

31:49.370 --> 31:51.280
to attack and plunder
the houses of our people.

31:51.290 --> 31:54.750
But all of you are
enjoying yourself here.

31:55.330 --> 31:58.190
You are wasting their hard-earned money
to entertain yourselves.

31:59.050 --> 32:00.750
Death is something you deserve.

32:01.610 --> 32:04.910
My arrow didn't pierce your heart
because the people of the northern city

32:04.970 --> 32:07.129
need you to come to their rescue.

32:07.130 --> 32:08.769
She's telling the truth.

32:08.770 --> 32:09.889
Many criminal gangs

32:09.890 --> 32:10.780
and hundreds of bandits

32:10.790 --> 32:13.640
have entered through the northern gate
under Official Wei's jurisdiction.

32:13.650 --> 32:15.549
They have been burning
the city for four hours.

32:15.550 --> 32:16.619
What?

32:16.620 --> 32:18.030
Why didn't you report it sooner?

32:18.710 --> 32:20.110
You told us

32:20.410 --> 32:21.950
that drinking is to be enjoyed.

32:22.290 --> 32:23.489
The sky won't fall.

32:23.490 --> 32:25.750
But your good mood will be gone
once it's ruined.

32:32.970 --> 32:35.089
As a man, you should admit
your mistake and punish yourself.

32:35.090 --> 32:36.430
Do you need me to help you?

32:37.010 --> 32:38.669
What bandits are you talking about?

32:38.670 --> 32:40.290
I don't know anything.

32:40.620 --> 32:43.089
I found this from the bandit
who was ordered to kill me.

32:43.090 --> 32:44.430
(Wei Tingyu)

32:45.090 --> 32:47.209
I bring this official badge with me
everywhere I go.

32:47.210 --> 32:48.590
How did the bandits get hold of it?

32:48.600 --> 32:50.809
The official badge needs
to be checked when the soldiers

32:50.810 --> 32:52.290
of the Military Command switch shifts.

32:52.300 --> 32:53.960
How did the Cangbei Gang
that loaned money

32:54.010 --> 32:55.630
to your mother-in-law get it?

32:56.050 --> 32:57.750
If you really know nothing of it,

32:58.090 --> 32:59.790
it means that your badge was stolen.

33:02.650 --> 33:04.310
Your Lordship,
something bad has happened.

33:04.320 --> 33:05.350
Something happened

33:05.370 --> 33:06.670
to Her Ladyship.

33:08.610 --> 33:09.750
Ming.

33:09.890 --> 33:11.369
Ming, I'm here.

33:11.370 --> 33:12.369
Wake up.

33:12.370 --> 33:13.510
Ming.

33:14.370 --> 33:15.750
Ming.

33:18.170 --> 33:19.310
Ming.

33:24.290 --> 33:25.870
Tingyu.

33:28.250 --> 33:29.950
I knew

33:31.410 --> 33:34.150
that you would come to me.

33:37.170 --> 33:38.950
Do you still remember

33:41.330 --> 33:46.110
what you told me when you sneaked

33:47.690 --> 33:49.449
into my courtyard back then?

33:49.450 --> 33:50.769
I do.

33:50.770 --> 33:52.289
The heaven will be my witness.

33:52.290 --> 33:53.910
I, Wei Tingyu, hereby vow

33:53.930 --> 33:56.870
that I'm willing to fire
all the maids in my residence.

33:57.010 --> 33:58.470
From now on,

33:59.810 --> 34:01.670
you will be the only woman I draw.

34:02.170 --> 34:03.289
If I break this vow,

34:03.290 --> 34:05.630
my heart will be punctured
and I'll die in the wild...

34:06.170 --> 34:07.680
Don't talk. I'll get you a physician.

34:07.690 --> 34:08.740
I'll get you a physician.

34:08.750 --> 34:11.129
Go and get me a physician!

34:11.130 --> 34:12.390
Tingyu.

34:12.450 --> 34:13.590
Ming.

34:14.330 --> 34:15.510
You said

34:16.970 --> 34:20.550
that I would be the only woman you drew.

34:20.810 --> 34:21.950
I know.

34:23.850 --> 34:25.929
If you break that vow…

34:25.930 --> 34:27.230
My heart will be punctured

34:27.890 --> 34:29.590
and I'll die in the wild.

34:31.650 --> 34:32.790
The curse

34:36.610 --> 34:38.470
has fallen on me

34:40.490 --> 34:41.950
and I have broken it

34:43.770 --> 34:45.110
for you.

35:00.570 --> 35:01.710
Ming.

35:03.090 --> 35:04.230
Ming.

35:04.730 --> 35:06.030
Ming.

35:12.970 --> 35:14.370
Ming.

35:26.730 --> 35:28.630
(Wealth and Luxury)
How dare them!

35:28.850 --> 35:30.590
Our country is at peace.

35:31.130 --> 35:33.870
But the bandits dared break into
the Duke of Ying's Residence.

35:34.010 --> 35:35.760
What was the Magistrate
of Shengtian doing?

35:35.770 --> 35:37.510
Where was the Military Command?

35:37.730 --> 35:38.870
Go.

35:39.160 --> 35:40.769
Bring me the Magistrate of Shengtian

35:40.770 --> 35:42.469
and the commanders

35:42.470 --> 35:43.790
of the Military Command.

35:43.810 --> 35:45.950
They dare rob
the Duke of Ying's Residence today,

35:46.170 --> 35:48.470
they'll rob me tomorrow.

35:50.450 --> 35:51.590
Your Majesty.

35:51.650 --> 35:54.110
Please give me the permission
to arrest the criminals.

35:56.970 --> 35:58.390
Bring me my sword.

36:00.690 --> 36:01.609
Song Mo.

36:01.610 --> 36:02.460
Yes, Your Majesty.

36:02.470 --> 36:04.550
Lead the Imperial Guard
to investigate this matter.

36:04.810 --> 36:06.470
Get to the bottom of it.

36:06.610 --> 36:08.480
Find out who was so bold enough

36:08.490 --> 36:10.289
to rob nobleman
who is serving the country.

36:10.290 --> 36:13.150
Find out who did this under my watch!

36:13.570 --> 36:15.110
Yes, Your Majesty.

36:19.130 --> 36:20.469
(Letter of Confession: I led the bandits
into the Capitol City and I regret it.)

36:20.470 --> 36:22.110
(This is my letter of confession.
I've sinned. Zhou Jiaxin.)

36:29.610 --> 36:32.990
It was always Madam who stayed
in touch with the bandits.

36:33.570 --> 36:35.630
I was just the messenger.

36:36.170 --> 36:37.710
I saw with my own eyes

36:38.050 --> 36:40.430
that she killed my mother-in-law.

36:41.010 --> 36:42.150
How dare you!

36:42.530 --> 36:43.689
You are her daughter-in-law.

36:43.690 --> 36:45.120
You used my name to commit this crime

36:45.130 --> 36:46.920
and now, you are trying
to shift the blame onto me.

36:46.930 --> 36:48.849
Nanny Zhou's
letter of confession is here.

36:48.850 --> 36:50.150
Are you going to deny it?

36:50.890 --> 36:52.190
Yingxue.

36:52.450 --> 36:54.889
Back then, I had a rough time
with my career.

36:54.890 --> 36:58.350
And you imitated others' handwriting
a few times to help me out.

36:58.490 --> 37:01.230
I can recognize your handwriting.

37:02.490 --> 37:03.630
Father.

37:05.650 --> 37:08.310
Two of the ministers
from the six ministries are here.

37:09.330 --> 37:10.470
Grand Secretary Wang.

37:10.970 --> 37:12.750
If you plead to His Majesty for mercy,

37:13.570 --> 37:14.870
I'll do the same

37:15.200 --> 37:17.990
to spare Yingxue
from getting the death penalty.

37:20.610 --> 37:22.390
I've doted on you so much

37:23.650 --> 37:27.030
that I've turned you into a monster.

37:28.170 --> 37:29.910
As your father,

37:30.050 --> 37:33.550
I doted on you because I felt guilty.

37:33.770 --> 37:35.849
But I've turned you into a monster

37:35.850 --> 37:38.310
who takes human lives lightly.

37:45.250 --> 37:48.950
I will ask His Majesty
to punish you severely.

37:50.730 --> 37:51.870
Xingyi.

37:52.170 --> 37:53.830
Calm down.

37:56.090 --> 37:57.830
Say no more.

37:57.970 --> 37:59.889
You just want me
to infuriate His Majesty

37:59.890 --> 38:02.870
over my daughter.

38:04.090 --> 38:06.150
I'll let you

38:07.490 --> 38:09.510
be the Grand Secretary.

38:09.820 --> 38:11.470
I've failed in disciplining my daughter.

38:12.130 --> 38:15.550
I will resign from His Majesty.

38:16.730 --> 38:20.470
As for the rest,
it's your family matter.

38:21.490 --> 38:22.870
You can do whatever you want.

38:25.170 --> 38:26.310
Father.

38:27.130 --> 38:28.049
If I die,

38:28.050 --> 38:30.710
the rest of your life
will be a nightmare.

38:30.760 --> 38:32.670
You'll regret it immensely, Father.

38:35.490 --> 38:36.950
What a sin.

38:37.530 --> 38:39.230
- What a sin!
- Father!

38:45.850 --> 38:47.929
I've done so much for you all my life.

38:47.930 --> 38:49.390
I didn't do anything wrong!

38:50.530 --> 38:52.550
We have both the witness
and the evidence here.

38:52.890 --> 38:54.870
You've been obsessed
with this your whole life.

38:55.450 --> 38:56.630
For what?

38:58.330 --> 38:59.470
Shiying.

39:00.650 --> 39:02.870
Are you going to force me
to admit to my crime too?

39:04.170 --> 39:06.630
What have I done wrong, Shiying?

39:07.530 --> 39:10.630
The government has had trouble
eliminating the Cangbei Gang,

39:10.930 --> 39:13.390
the Chimen Gang, and the Five Yamas.

39:13.730 --> 39:15.350
And it's all because of you.

39:16.490 --> 39:19.950
Leading the bandits into the city
is unheard of.

39:20.930 --> 39:22.070
Yingxue.

39:22.290 --> 39:25.630
Don't drag us down with you
if you seek death.

39:27.170 --> 39:28.950
Just admit to your crime.

39:29.890 --> 39:31.070
(Military Command)

39:33.510 --> 39:34.730
No.

39:36.310 --> 39:37.950
Wei Tingzhen holds

39:39.070 --> 39:40.630
half of the capital money.

39:41.340 --> 39:44.870
The Duke of Jing's residence
is Her Majesty's original family.

39:45.170 --> 39:47.249
Her brother is the one
who lost his official badge.

39:47.250 --> 39:48.409
Are you trying to ruin

39:48.410 --> 39:50.590
the reputation of the royal family
by doing so?

39:50.930 --> 39:52.630
Think about it.

39:52.810 --> 39:55.550
Why isn't Wei Tingzhen here yet?

39:57.290 --> 39:58.550
The Wei family

39:58.610 --> 40:00.510
can break its ties with me.

40:00.770 --> 40:02.230
But you can't.

40:03.090 --> 40:04.630
If you force me to admit to my crime,

40:04.690 --> 40:05.830
fine.

40:06.170 --> 40:07.129
I'll admit

40:07.130 --> 40:09.630
that I committed treason
that will wipe out the entire family!

40:10.450 --> 40:11.289
You have gone mad!

40:11.290 --> 40:13.809
How dare you say you committed treason?

40:13.810 --> 40:15.150
Why not?

40:15.890 --> 40:18.350
I did everything for the Dou family
my whole life.

40:18.810 --> 40:20.630
Now, you want to get me killed.

40:20.930 --> 40:23.129
Why shouldn't I drag you down with me?

40:23.130 --> 40:23.979
You!

40:23.980 --> 40:25.140
Yingxue.

40:27.050 --> 40:28.710
The first person got killed
because of you

40:30.770 --> 40:32.070
is Ming.

41:08.570 --> 41:10.070
Father knows

41:10.230 --> 41:11.990
that you are taking good care
of the family.

41:13.150 --> 41:14.730
I'm indeed useless.

41:14.930 --> 41:16.339
But I don't want you

41:16.340 --> 41:18.390
to risk so much for me.

41:19.770 --> 41:21.710
If I can't be together with him forever,

41:22.570 --> 41:24.230
I'll meet him in the afterlife.

41:26.930 --> 41:28.230
If the bandits were not here,

41:28.890 --> 41:30.670
no one would've died.

41:31.850 --> 41:33.510
- This is karma.
- Ming.

41:34.090 --> 41:35.649
I'm sure you know

41:35.650 --> 41:37.870
- Ming.
- whose sin it is.

41:39.410 --> 41:40.550
Ming.

41:40.570 --> 41:42.230
You are still alive, right?

41:42.730 --> 41:43.870
Ming.

41:43.930 --> 41:46.030
Look at me.

41:46.690 --> 41:48.910
I'm your mother.

41:50.210 --> 41:51.390
This is their fault.

41:52.110 --> 41:53.470
This is their fault.

41:53.690 --> 41:56.710
They are forcing me
to admit to my crime, Ming.

41:57.070 --> 41:59.850
Wake up, Ming.

42:00.010 --> 42:01.150
Be good.

42:01.210 --> 42:04.670
Ming, wake up. Ming.

42:10.890 --> 42:13.590
I didn't kill you.

42:14.690 --> 42:16.070
It's them.

42:16.290 --> 42:17.889
You are dead because of them!

42:17.890 --> 42:21.110
Now, they want to kill me too, Ming!

42:21.650 --> 42:23.190
Greed is your downfall.

42:23.890 --> 42:25.630
You know who killed her.

42:26.410 --> 42:27.870
This is not the end yet.

42:28.290 --> 42:29.430
Dou Zhao.

42:30.330 --> 42:32.009
I'm not the only one in the Capital

42:32.010 --> 42:33.670
who wants you dead.

42:34.050 --> 42:36.270
I'll make you live a life of suffering

42:36.370 --> 42:38.110
forever!

42:47.050 --> 42:48.510
She has gone mad.

42:49.050 --> 42:50.190
Take her away.

43:24.810 --> 43:26.289
Our relationship will be bound by love

43:26.290 --> 43:27.910
and we'll stay united forever.

43:28.050 --> 43:29.190
Dear.

43:29.210 --> 43:31.190
Do you think it'll come true for us?

43:31.450 --> 43:32.529
The bandits are vicious.

43:32.530 --> 43:33.969
You have to come back safe and sound

43:33.970 --> 43:35.049
and with victory.

43:35.050 --> 43:39.520
♪Forsaking words of farewell♪

43:40.260 --> 43:42.930
♪The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon♪

43:43.540 --> 43:46.640
♪In this life, oh♪

43:46.790 --> 43:48.469
♪Without you♪

43:48.470 --> 43:52.090
♪What is there to envy?♪

43:52.550 --> 43:55.029
♪Let me lay down
my blade and leave the sea of battles♪

43:55.030 --> 43:59.349
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

43:59.350 --> 44:01.539
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

44:01.540 --> 44:05.990
♪Bloom in a single night for you♪

44:06.140 --> 44:09.269
♪The splendor of the world is
but fleeting sorrow♪

44:09.270 --> 44:12.360
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

44:12.700 --> 44:15.949
♪I shall hold your hand♪

44:15.950 --> 44:18.929
♪And walk through the dust♪

44:18.930 --> 44:21.139
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

44:21.140 --> 44:25.429
♪Leaving the world behind♪

44:25.430 --> 44:27.739
♪From now on,
all the vast wonders of the world♪

44:27.740 --> 44:31.989
♪May be left as blank spaces♪

44:31.990 --> 44:35.690
♪The dazzling spring moon over the city♪

44:35.870 --> 44:38.930
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

44:39.100 --> 44:44.310
♪Why ascend to high towers again?♪

44:45.110 --> 44:47.369
♪I will lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

44:47.370 --> 44:49.009
♪Break my spear to crown you♪

44:49.010 --> 44:51.729
♪With a golden-branch hairpin♪

44:51.730 --> 44:53.849
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

44:53.850 --> 44:57.959
♪Bloom for you♪

44:57.960 --> 45:01.720
♪No more guarding lonely towers♪

45:01.760 --> 45:05.079
♪Spring is near, ripe for the taking♪

45:05.080 --> 45:06.419
♪Holding your hand♪

45:06.420 --> 45:11.370
♪Till we reach beyond the noise♪

45:11.810 --> 45:14.960
♪Only for you, I shall paint♪

45:15.150 --> 45:17.940
♪With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

45:18.130 --> 45:19.979
♪And for all else♪

45:19.980 --> 45:26.970
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

45:29.370 --> 45:30.409
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:30.410 --> 45:31.329
(Every medical behavior involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:31.330 --> 45:32.590
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
